        `},{id:"prosthetics-care",title:"Caring for Dentures and Extending Their Service Life",seoTitle:"Caring for Dental Prosthetics — How to Extend Lifespan and Maintain Comfort",img:w["05_care.jpg"]||"",image_description:`
          <p>
